{"tid":780349,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿里被揭曾與人妻發展不倫戀","createTime":"2018-08-15T05:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T06:01:18.000Z","uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5260645dac6fb088a61ef5ba3e63a41afc52459","tid":780349,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=bzEgjJDypzABWqFO%2B20nl9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=cb5740c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】家花不及野花香？熱刺球星迪利阿里雖有美艷女友，但日前被人夫踢爆明撩其中女艷妻，令人想入非非。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》披露，今年22歲的迪利阿里（Dele Alli），與40歲大胸「膠樣」艷星派絲（Katie Price），疑似有不尋常關係。31歲的基倫是派絲的丈夫，曾經是脫衣舞男，他受訪時表示：「回家之後，我發現阿里同她玩Facetime，當時Katie已睡著，我偷看了她的手機，當我接電話時，他把手機鏡頭移往另一邊，似乎另有內情。」<br />\n<br />\n「我倆沒有對話，但我當時已經很生氣，因我從來不知道他們是認識的。」然而，基倫透露事件發生在幾年前，意味著當時阿里仍是單身，但派絲已公開表示阿里就是她的白馬王子。<br />\n<br />\n派絲曾與前曼聯前鋒約基相戀，育有1子，已公開的「戰績」至少有兩名戀人是足球員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46752cc37c7840692bda1f0e17d516732cb3381a","tid":780349,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-prod.gloucestershirelive.co.uk/incoming/article1169464.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200/katie-price.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.gloucestershirelive.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle1169464.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs1200%2Fkatie-price.jpg&h=058e84b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171021/s00007/6ee46430991ab1521e74f906bd9c7af9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171021%2Fs00007%2F6ee46430991ab1521e74f906bd9c7af9.jpg&h=1980de0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"911ba4547c6e720d305ff7be4cd2fbd73a365dc6","tid":780349,"uid":154872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/katie-pr